Name: The Maze VR
About the game: The Maze VR You can play The Maze VR with up to 8 people. Race, Punch, Grab, Shoot and Think your way through each challenge. If you solve the VR Room you can choose one of the doors to progress further into The Maze and find your teamplayers to unlock the Big Master Multiplayer Room. Share knowledge about the rooms and try to get the best The Maze time ever! We now support LIV! We are curious about the great video's you'll produce with this amazing feature :)
